OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA clear
OL,6,Fnight to start with light winds, but
OL,7,Fpatchy cloud developing from the east.
OL,8,FSome mist and fog forming in prone
OL,9,Fclear spots, with a grass frost in
OL,10,Fplaces.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FAny mist, fog and low cloud
OL,13,Fwill clear quickly after sunrise.
OL,14,FAnother bright and sunny day expected
OL,15,Fwith temperatures slightly higher than
OL,16,FThursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
